sequenceDiagram
  %% ==========================================================
  %% A) Typical FastAPI request turn
  %% ==========================================================
  autonumber
  actor User
  participant API as api.py endpoint
  participant Workflow as WorkflowService
  participant StateDB as SQLite sessions.state
  participant Runtime as services/*_runtime.py
  participant Agent as root_agent
  participant Tools as Tools/AgentTools

  User->>API: POST /api/projects/{id}/vision/generate
  API->>Workflow: get_session_status(session_id)
  Workflow->>StateDB: read current state
  Workflow-->>API: normalized state
  API->>Runtime: run_*_agent_from_state(state, user_input)
  Runtime->>Agent: execute deterministic phase runtime
  Agent->>Tools: tool call(s) (optional)
  Tools-->>Agent: tool response(s) (optional)
  Agent-->>Runtime: structured result
  Runtime-->>API: artifact payload + completion metadata
  alt state transition required
    API->>Workflow: update_session_status(session_id, partial_update)
    Workflow->>StateDB: persist state
  else no transition required
    API->>API: return current state snapshot
  end
  API-->>User: JSON response
